## San Francisco

San Francisco is a vibrant city located in California, on a peninsula between the Pacific Ocean and San Francisco Bay.The city is best known for its hilly terrain, eclectic architecture, and historical landmarks. It operates under a city-county government in which legislative authority lies with an elected board of supervisors. The population of San Francisco grew exponentially in the 19th century as people came in droves during the height of the Gold Rush. This is also how the San Francisco 49ers got their name. In terms of its economy, the city is known for hosting the headquarters for many major financial and technological companies[^1].

[^1]: @R2023

