## Why SF?

I chose San Francisco as I was born in the San Francisco Bay Area and I have a lot of family there as well. I visited most recently in December 2022, and while I have no desire to move there at this point in my life, I find the city to be beautiful and the culture is very interesting. There is no way anyone can be bored here, as there is always something new to do.

